{"tid":2312673,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國人糧食危機？居然跟「死對頭印度」買稻米","createTime":"2020-12-05T07:09:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-05T12:29:03.000Z","uid":41343,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"7f50beed2274b18264d73f34d6cb6cd87b248793","tid":2312673,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T07:09:26.000Z","msg":"中國官媒先前宣稱國今年豐收。近日卻有印度官員表示，中共當局30年來首度向印進口大量稻米、穀物。由於今年中印兩國，於西藏邊境地帶發生多起大規模武裝衝突，關係陷入前所未見的緊張。外界不禁猜測，當前中國社會是否面臨糧食危機？<br />\n<br />\n中國向來礙於品質問題，避免從印度採購稻米，加上目前中方與印度緊張關係未解。不過，根據《路透社》報導，印度稻米出口協會主席黑天．羅（BV Krishna Rao）透露，中國在今年開始向印度進口稻米，而且明年可能還會持續進口，甚至增加購買量。<br />\n<br />\n《自由亞洲電台》分析，中國今年受到疫情與疫情、蝗災、洪水等多重破壞，稻穀產量大減，導致目前中國米糧在供應市場均已漲價。中共政府雖未公佈實際數字，但中國媒體推測，今年全球糧食產量降幅恐已達30%。<br />\n<br />\n印度稻米貿易官員指出，向來中國的稻米購買對象泰國、越南、緬甸和巴基斯坦等國，今年剩餘的供應量有限，與印度價格相比，每噸報價至少高出30美元。<br />\n<br />\n印度農業部門官員則透露，雙方簽下貿易合約，以離岸價（FOB）每噸300美元價格出口10萬噸大米，合約總價為3000萬美元（約新台幣8億4590萬元），近期已經由海運送往中國。這也是中國30年來首次向印度進口稻米。"},{"pid":"3c8c6363baebc500f4b8d304636d41f0a4d629e9","tid":2312673,"uid":7323,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T07:13:01.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">呢啲咪叫賤格囉</span>"},{"pid":"b941f5a1f4d3c930651e3743ad66f2b411c5ca8f","tid":2312673,"uid":277296,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T07:16:32.000Z","msg":"又話食草既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0b03c186840e8cc6509cc3e027c9310f0616419","tid":2312673,"uid":280593,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T07:19:57.000Z","msg":"喪權辱國<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de671c39327397e6d948dc3d7d2662416e5bfabe","tid":2312673,"uid":32983,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T07:21:36.000Z","msg":"食邊到米就係邊到人<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/throw.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67188a4d55e0ffb292eda471400fd04d0e7344f1","tid":2312673,"uid":113929,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T07:24:30.000Z","msg":"買哂敵人d糧食，等敵軍餓死，不戰而屈人之兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21a035965aed4b0d68f50d19d62ada7c3d0d53ee","tid":2312673,"uid":70786,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T07:25:15.000Z","msg":"支那人：要不是咱們吃你的印度米，你們全都完蛋啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c65b619a4201beb1f87c11a4ad336bd906de0e6","tid":2312673,"uid":321002,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T07:25:22.000Z","msg":"雜草豐收？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"669bf47df30245ab42a743d0e57d03cfa8354dfb","tid":2312673,"uid":126317,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a0b03c186840e8cc6509cc3e027c9310f0616419","tid":2312673,"uid":280593,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T07:19:57.000Z","msg":"喪權辱國<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T07:29:13.000Z","msg":"中國人骨氣何在？<br />\n説好的戰狼呢？共產黨為何突然變左隻乞兒犬？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"807b845dc2a1c2024fe38330d2e483fa46b41d13","tid":2312673,"uid":301952,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T07:30:38.000Z","msg":"公道講<br />\n八九成國家係支那死對頭架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6332505a197a619a0f4dc9c2e85c0df77994cd2","tid":2312673,"uid":54337,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T07:30:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n戰狼呢"},{"pid":"54024ff1195a014d9725c7f63c00